		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm not sure whether I figured out what's going on? It looks like you're picking the order in which units go into battle? Looks reasonable...<br /><br />As an aside, one thing that will help with the clarity of NES videos on youtube is to upscale your input with nearest-neighbor 2x before uploading; otherwise the mpeg artifacts make a blurry mess of everything.

		

		</td>
